  }
  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Initiating Lake Panel Design**\n\nI\'m starting on the core Databricks data lake simulator module, specifically `/src/components/DatabricksLakePanel.tsx`. This dashboard module is absolutely critical, and I\'m really excited to begin working on it. It\'s a high-value, sophisticated visual component, and I\'m eager to build it.\n\n\n**Defining Lake Panel Features**\n\nI\'ve decided on the core features for the Databricks Lake Panel: an interactive Medallion Pipeline Visualizer and a Databricks Spark Code Snippet Generator. The visualizer will show Bronze, Silver, and Gold layers of the lake, with detailed metrics for each. I\'m focusing on making the visualization interactive and informative, including code snippets generation.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I will create `/src/components/DatabricksLakePanel.tsx` to serve as the core Databricks Exploration module. This panel features an interactive Medallion Pipeline Visualizer, PySpark ETL merge loaders, custom SQL playground sandbox that queries real operational data in-memory, and CSV/JSON ingestion download links."
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 3
      nanos: 99208507
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
